WEBVTT

00:02:59.812 --> 00:03:01.935
In fact, the original research study

00:03:01.935 --> 00:03:03.934
that suggested that was the case

00:03:03.934 --> 00:03:06.809
was completely fraudulent.

00:03:06.809 --> 00:03:09.985
It was actually retracted from the journal Lancet,

00:03:09.985 --> 00:03:11.577
in which it was published,

00:03:11.577 --> 00:03:13.467
and that author, a physician,

00:03:13.467 --> 00:03:16.721
had his medical license taken away from him.

00:03:16.721 --> 00:03:20.675
(Applause)

00:03:20.675 --> 00:03:22.257
The Institute of Medicine,

00:03:22.257 --> 00:03:23.820
The Centers for Disease Control,

00:03:23.820 --> 00:03:26.164
have repeatedly investigated this

00:03:26.164 --> 00:03:29.771
and there is no credible evidence

00:03:29.771 --> 00:03:32.456
that vaccines cause autism.